<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Feedback Received</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4299e1 0%, #3182ce 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .priority-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .priority-low { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); }
        .priority-medium { background: rgba(237, 137, 54, 0.9); }
        .priority-high { background: rgba(245, 101, 101, 0.9); }
        .priority-critical { background: rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.9); border: 2px solid #fff; }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .feedback-card {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .feedback-header {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .feedback-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        
        .feedback-type {
            background: #4299e1;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .feedback-type.positive { background: #48bb78; }
        .feedback-type.negative { background: #f56565; }
        .feedback-type.suggestion { background: #ed8936; }
        .feedback-type.bug { background: #e53e3e; }
        .feedback-type.feature_request { background: #9f7aea; }
        
        .rating {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .stars {
            color: #f6ad55;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .feedback-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }
        
        .feedback-content {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4299e1;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        .submitter-info {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        
        .avatar {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .submitter-details h4 {
            margin: 0 0 4px 0;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .submitter-details p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .context-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .context-item {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .context-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .context-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .tracking-info {
            background: #edf2f7;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .tracking-id {
            font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', 'Roboto Mono', Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #4299e1;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #3182ce;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #e2e8f0;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #cbd5e0;
        }
        
        .btn-respond {
            background: #48bb78;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-respond:hover {
            background: #38a169;
        }
        
        .action-tip {
            background: #f0fff4;
            border-left: 4px solid #48bb78;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .action-tip.bug {
            background: #fef5e7;
            border-left-color: #f6ad55;
        }
        
        .action-tip.negative {
            background: #fed7d7;
            border-left-color: #f56565;
        }
        
        .action-tip h4 {
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .action-tip.bug h4 { color: #c05621; }
        .action-tip.negative h4 { color: #742a2a; }
        .action-tip h4 { color: #22543d; }
        
        .action-tip p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .action-tip.bug p { color: #744210; }
        .action-tip.negative p { color: #742a2a; }
        .action-tip p { color: #276749; }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .context-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .feedback-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            
            .submitter-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .priority-indicator {
                position: static;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {{#if priority}}
            <div class="priority-indicator priority-{{priority}}">
                {{#ifEquals priority 'critical'}}üö®{{/ifEquals}} {{uppercase priority}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            <h1>New Feedback üìù</h1>
            <p>A user has submitted feedback that requires your attention</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{recipientName}},
            </div>
            
            <p>You've received new feedback about <strong>{{featureName}}</strong> in {{applicationName}}. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="feedback-card">
                <div class="feedback-header">
                    <div class="feedback-meta">
                        <span class="feedback-type {{feedbackType}}">{{uppercase feedbackType}}</span>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <span class="stars">{{ratingStars}}</span>
                            <span>{{rating}}/5</span>
                        </div>
                        {{#if category}}
                        <span style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px;">{{category}}</span>
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feedback-body">
                    <div class="feedback-content">
                        {{feedbackContent}}
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="submitter-info">
                        <div class="avatar">{{substring submitterName 0 1}}</div>
                        <div class="submitter-details">
                            <h4>{{submitterName}}</h4>
                            <p>{{submitterEmail}}{{#if submitterRole}} ‚Ä¢ {{submitterRole}}{{/if}}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="context-grid">
                <div class="context-item">
                    <div class="context-label">Application</div>
                    <div class="context-value">{{applicationName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="context-item">
                    <div class="context-label">Feature</div>
                    <div class="context-value">{{featureName}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if environment}}
                <div class="context-item">
                    <div class="context-label">Environment</div>
                    <div class="context-value">{{uppercase environment}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if version}}
                <div class="context-item">
                    <div class="context-label">Version</div>
                    <div class="context-value">{{version}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="context-item">
                    <div class="context-label">Submitted</div>
                    <div class="context-value">{{submissionDate}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if trackingId}}
            <div class="tracking-info">
                <strong>üìã Reference ID:</strong> <span class="tracking-id">{{trackingId}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                {{#if dashboardUrl}}
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">üìä View Dashboard</a>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if respondUrl}}
                <a href="{{respondUrl}}" class="btn btn-respond">üí¨ Respond</a>
                {{/if}}
                <a href="mailto:{{submitterEmail}}?subject=Re: Your feedback about {{featureName}}&body=Hi {{submitterName}},%0D%0A%0D%0AThank you for your feedback about {{featureName}}." class="btn btn-secondary">‚úâÔ∏è Email User</a>
            </div>
            
            {{#ifEquals feedbackType 'bug'}}
            <div class="action-tip bug">
                <h4>üêõ Suggested Actions</h4>
                <p>Verify and reproduce the issue ‚Ä¢ Create a support ticket ‚Ä¢ Assign to appropriate developer ‚Ä¢ Keep user informed of progress</p>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            {{#ifEquals feedbackType 'feature_request'}}
            <div class="action-tip">
                <h4>üí° Suggested Actions</h4>
                <p>Evaluate feasibility and business impact ‚Ä¢ Add to product roadmap ‚Ä¢ Discuss with product team ‚Ä¢ Update user on timeline</p>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            {{#ifEquals feedbackType 'negative'}}
            <div class="action-tip negative">
                <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Suggested Actions</h4>
                <p>Reach out to understand pain points ‚Ä¢ Identify improvement opportunities ‚Ä¢ Consider priority based on impact ‚Ä¢ Follow up with resolution</p>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            <p>The user has been notified that their feedback was received and that your team will review it.</p>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p>Best regards,<br><strong>{{companyName}} Feedback System</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{formatDate submissionDate}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Feedback from: {{submitterEmail}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 